OL,3,CHumza Yousaf resigns as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister
OL,6,FHis resignation will now trigger an
OL,7,FSNP leadership contest, but Mr Yousaf
OL,8,Fconfirmed he will continue to serve in
OL,9,Foffice in the interim until a suitable
OL,10,Freplacement is found.
OL,12,FIt comes after days of tumultuous
OL,13,Ffighting cross-party following the
OL,14,Fcollapse of a power-sharing deal
OL,15,Fbetween the SNP and Scottish Greens on
OL,16,FThursday.
