OL,4,Cfirst minister
OL,6,FWhile he said it was "the right
OL,7,Fdecision", he added: "Unfortunately in
OL,8,Fending the Bute House Agreement in the
OL,9,Fmatter I did I clearly underestimate
OL,10,Fthe level of hurt and upset that
OL,11,Fcaused Green colleagues.
OL,13,F"For a minority government to be able
OL,14,Fto govern effectively trust when
OL,15,Fworking with the opposition is clearly
OL,16,Ffundamental."
OL,18,FHe added a route through the no-
OL,19,Fconfidence vote was "absolutely
OL,20,Fpossible".
