OL,6,FBut he added: "I am not willing to
OL,7,Ftrade in my values or principles or do
OL,8,Fdeals with whomever simply for
OL,9,Fretaining power."
OL,11,FMr Yousaf was facing a vote of
OL,12,Fconfidence, tabled by the Scottish
OL,13,FConservatives, while Scottish Labour
OL,14,Ftabled one for the Scottish Government
OL,15,Fas a whole.
OL,17,FVotes on the motions were expected at
OL,18,FHolyrood in the coming week.
