OL,3,CHumza Yousaf resigns as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister
OL,6,FMr Yousaf previously said he would not
OL,7,Fresign and he intended to win the
OL,8,Fconfidence votes.
OL,10,FSupport for the SNP declined after the
OL,11,Fparty backed legislation to make it
OL,12,Feasier for people to change their
OL,13,Fgender, and implemented a hate crime
OL,14,Flaw that made transgender identity a
OL,15,Fprotected characteristic, even though
OL,16,Fthe same protections weren't given to
OL,17,Fall women.
OL,19,FThen came Mr Yousaf's decision to
OL,20,Fscrap the 2030 target for greenhouse
OL,21,Fgas reductions.
