OL,3,CHumza Yousaf resigns as Scotland's
OL,4,Cfirst minister
OL,6,FHe had been elected to succeed the
OL,7,Foperation after Nicola Sturgeon
OL,8,Fresigned from the position in March
OL,9,Flast year, becoming the sixth first
OL,10,Fminister.
OL,12,FMs Sturgeon's resignation came amid a
OL,13,Fpolice investigation into allegations
OL,14,Fthat the party had misused money
OL,15,Fdonated to fund a second independence
OL,16,Freferendum.JMs Sturgeon was questioned
OL,17,Fand released without being charged
OL,18,Flast June. Her husband, former SNP
OL,19,Ftreasurer Peter Murrell, was charged
OL,20,Fwith embezzlement earlier this month.
OL,21,FBoth deny any wrongdoing in the case.
